quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,Tendereza erinnya ly’omulabiriziwo owa waggulu
  87,2,Oyo eyatonda n'atereeza
  87,3,Era eyateekateeka buli kintu n'akyenkanyankanya
  87,4,Era oyo ameza omuddo oguliibwa e bisolo
  87,5,Oluvanyuma agufuula omukalu
  87,6,Tujja kukusomesa (Kur'ani) obeere nga teweerabira
  87,7,Okugyako ebyo Katonda by’anaaba ayagadde okukwerabiza. Katonda y’amanyi ebyogerwa mu lwatu ne mu kyama
  87,8,Tujja kukwanguyiza amateeka gabeere mangu
  87,9,"Kale buulirira, okubuulirira bwe kuba nga kunaagasa"
  87,10,Anaaganyulwa oyo atya Katonda
  87,11,Omwonoonyi ajja ku kwesamba (okubuulirira okwo)
  87,12,Oyo alyesogga omuliro ogwamaanyi
  87,13,"Ng’amaze (okusonsekebwa mu muliro ogwo), tagenda kufa wadde okufuna obulamu (obwesiimisa)"
  87,14,Mazima yeesiimye omuntu e yeetukuza
  87,15,N’ayogera ku linnya ly’omuleziwe olwo nno n’asaala
  87,16,Wabula mmwe musukkulumya obulamu obw’ensi
  87,17,So nga obulamu obw'enkomerero bwe businga obulungi era bwe bwo kusigalawo
  87,18,Mazima bino biri mu biwandiiko ebyasooka
  87,19,Ebiwandiiko bya Ibrahim ne Musa
  88,1,Abaffe wali ofunye okunyumizibwa ku kibuutikira (eky’olunaku lw'enkomerero)
  88,2,Olunaku olwo ebyenyi bigenda kuba nga biswavu
  88,3,"Nga bitawaana, nga bikoowu"
  88,4,Nga byesonseka omuliro ogwengeredde
  88,5,Bigenda kunywesebwa ku luzzi olweseze
  88,6,(Abantu abo) tebagenda kubeera na kya kulya kyonna okugyako e miti egy’amaggwa
  88,7,Egitaliimu kiriisa wadde okuwonya e njala
  88,8,Ebyenyi e birala bigenda kubeera mu byengera
  88,9,Bigenda kusiima olw’okutakabana kwa byo
  88,10,Nga biri mu jjana ey’awaggulu
  88,11,Togenda kuwulira mu yo bigambo bya butaliimu
  88,12,Mu jjana mulimu e nsulo e zikulukuta
  88,13,Era nga mulimu ebitanda ebisitufu (Ebiwunde)
  88,14,N’ebikopo ebinywerwamu ebitegekeddwa
  88,15,N’emitto egisimbiddwa ennyiriri
  88,16,N’ebyaliiro nga byanjuluziddwa
  88,17,Abaffe tebatunuulira (olutunuulira olw’okuyiga) engamiya ngeri ki bwe yatondebwa
  88,18,N’eggulu nga bwe lyasitulwa
  88,19,N’ensozi engeri gye zaasimbwamu
  88,20,N’ensi engeri gye yaseetezebwamu
  88,21,Kale nno buulirira gwe (Nabbi Muhammad) kubanga oli mubuulirizi
  88,22,Toliiwo kubakaka
  88,23,Naye abo abanaava ku bigambobyo ne bajeema
  88,24,Katonda agenda okubabonereza e bibonerezo e bisinga okuba e bikakali
  88,25,Mazima ddala gyetuli y’eri obuddo bwabwe
  88,26,Oluvanyuma ddala okubalibwa kwabwe kuli ku ffe
  89,1,Ndayira e mambya
  89,2,N’ebiro e kkumi
  89,3,N’ebibiri bibiri n’ebyensusuuba
  89,4,N’ekiro bwekiba nga kitambula (nga kijja oba nga kivaawo)
  89,5,Abaffe mu kulayira kuno temuliimu kwebuulirira eri oyo alina amagezi
  89,6,Tewamanya ebyo Omuleziwo (Katonda) bye yatuusa ku bantu b'ekika kya A'adi
  89,7,Aba-Irama abawagguufu
  89,8,Tewatondebwangayo babafaanana mu nsi
  89,9,N’ebyo bye yatuusa ku ba Thamuud abaawukuulanga e njazi mu lusenyi
  89,10,N'ebyo bye yatuusa ku Firaawo nannyini nkondo
  89,11,Abo bonna (aboogeddwako) beewaggula kuno ku nsi
  89,12,Ne bayitiriza nnyo obwonoonefu
  89,13,Omuleziwo (Katonda) kye yava abafukirira e bibonerezo e by'enjawulo
  89,14,Mazima ddala Omuleziwo (Katonda) abalindiridde
  89,15,"Wabula omuntu, Omuleziwe (Katonda) bw'amugezesa n'amugabira e birungi, omuntu oyo agamba nti Katonda wange ampadde"
  89,16,Ku ludda olulala bw'aba amugezesezza n'amufundiza ebyenfunaye agamba nti omulezi wange (Katonda) anzikakkanyiza
  89,17,"Nedda, wabula temuyisa bulungi ba Mulekwa"
  89,18,Era temwekubiriza kuliisa banaku
  89,19,"Ate nga mulya emmaali ya ba Mulekwa, olulya olugimalawo"
  89,20,Era nga mwagala eby'enfuna okwagala okuyitiridde
  89,21,"Nedda eyo si y'endaba e ntuufu ey’ebintu, e nsi bwe ribeera nga ebetenteddwa"
  89,22,Omuleziwo n'ajja nga ne Ba Malayika basimbye ennyiriri
  89,23,"Era kwolwo o muliro Jahannama gulireetebwa, kwolwo nno omuntu alijjukira (bye yakola ku nsi) naye okujjukira kuno kugenda ku mugasaaki"
  89,24,"Agenda kugamba: zinsanze nze. Singa nategekera obulamu bwange buno"
  89,25,Olunaku olwo (Katonda) e bibonerezo by'agenda okubonereza nabyo tewali n'omu yali abibonerezzaako
  89,26,Era ensiba gyalisiba ku lunaku olwo tewali yali agisibyeko
  89,27,Owange ggwe omwoyo omutebenkevu (omuntu)
  89,28,Dda eri Omuleziwo ng'oli musanyufu era asiimiddwa
  89,29,Olwo nno oyingire mu baddu bange (abalongoofu)
  89,30,Era oyingire mu jjana yange